#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdocument-composer.md:92
msgid ""
"**Language** — ISO 639-1 dropdown. Persisted as the `language` column on "
"`document_templates`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdocument-composer.md:93
msgid ""
"**Organization** — free-text input with autocomplete. Persisted as the "
"`organization` column."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdocument-composer.md:95
msgid ""
"Both live on the `DocumentTemplate` wrapper, not inside the `zones` object."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdocument-composer.md:97
msgid ""
"The list panel toolbar offers search and language filtering; documents are "
"grouped under collapsible organization headers, identical to the BPMN and "
"Form list patterns."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdocument-composer.md:99
msgid ""
"Pending-until-Save: typing language or organization updates the editor's "
"draft but does not regroup the document until **Save** is clicked. A load-"
"window guard suppresses synthetic `onTemplateChange` events fired by child "
"editors (TipTap) during document load, so opening a document no longer flips "
"`hasChanges` spuriously."
msgstr ""

